This class implements a LogWriter. This writer will write all the log messages it receives to an internal structure. The whole internal structure can be sent to an formatter when the getLogEntries() method is called. 
@package Debug
@link http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/lesser.html}

Writes a log entry to the internal memory structure. 
@param string $group
@param array $logData

