ezcDebugFormatterHTML class implements a HTML debug formatter in order to create from the Timer and Writer datastructures HTML.  This class implements the ezcDebugFormatter interface. 
@package Debug
@link http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/lesser.html}

Every class that implements this interface can be used to format timer and writer data to a string. 
@package Debug
@link http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/lesser.html}

Returns an string containing the formatted output. 
@param array $timerData
@param array $writerData
